      <guid>https://www.newsdeeply.com/womenandgirls/community/2017/05/09/sex-education-programs-in-kenyan-schools-are-failing-students</guid>
      <description>A recent survey of teachers and students found that Kenyan schools are not teaching sexuality education properly. This has serious consequences for girls, who risk early pregnancy and the transmission of STIs or HIV if they’re taught abstinence is the only way.</description>
